WEBVTT

01:32.210 --> 01:34.940
[How dare you!?]

01:35.020 --> 01:39.940
[Episode 22]

01:47.560 --> 01:50.020
His Majesty didn't attend court yesterday.

01:50.310 --> 01:52.170
Is he not attending today either?

01:53.120 --> 01:54.039
I've heard that

01:54.640 --> 01:56.840
not only was Her Majesty
severely injured,

01:56.840 --> 01:58.170
but even His Majesty...

02:01.200 --> 02:02.270
If that's true,

02:02.290 --> 02:04.760
how can we possibly compete
against Prince Duan's faction?

02:04.760 --> 02:05.640
All right.

02:06.590 --> 02:08.360
Both of you, keep your voices down.

02:08.360 --> 02:09.960
Don't frighten yourselves.

02:12.710 --> 02:13.240
Lord Jia.

02:14.400 --> 02:15.710
From what I've heard,

02:16.360 --> 02:17.120
His Majesty

02:17.590 --> 02:19.150
will not be able to come,

02:19.680 --> 02:20.540
as we expected.

02:22.280 --> 02:24.120
This is precisely

02:24.590 --> 02:26.850
our golden opportunity to rise to power.

02:27.030 --> 02:28.280
But why isn't

02:28.910 --> 02:30.570
Prince Duan showing his face?

02:30.910 --> 02:31.910
You're asking me?

02:32.800 --> 02:34.000
Who should I ask then?

02:34.360 --> 02:36.590
Prince Duan trusts you the most.

02:37.840 --> 02:40.100
His Highness also trusted Zhao Wucheng.

02:40.280 --> 02:40.840
Wasn't he

02:41.470 --> 02:44.070
assassinated at the street corner
yesterday?

02:45.030 --> 02:46.120
Lord Zhao is dead?

02:52.150 --> 02:53.560
Today's court session

02:54.150 --> 02:56.120
is like walking into a trap.

02:57.560 --> 02:59.180
We might not be able

02:59.280 --> 03:01.030
to stay alive.

03:03.430 --> 03:05.030
Lord Mu's scheme

03:06.000 --> 03:08.240
has put us in a terrible position.

03:50.360 --> 03:53.190
I haven't practiced my makeup skills
for a long time.

03:53.190 --> 03:53.910
I'm rusty.

03:55.000 --> 03:56.530
Let me do your makeup again.

03:56.710 --> 03:58.040
That's enough, Wanyin.

03:59.710 --> 04:01.440
You've already redone it once.

04:03.560 --> 04:04.470
Are you tired?

04:05.150 --> 04:05.750
Not at all.

04:12.840 --> 04:14.840
I think it looks quite good now.

04:15.800 --> 04:17.600
I don't look as haggard anymore.

04:20.240 --> 04:21.040
No.

04:22.360 --> 04:23.310
In court,

04:23.750 --> 04:25.750
dozens of eyes will be watching you,

04:25.920 --> 04:27.980
each person with countless schemes.

04:28.040 --> 04:30.570
We absolutely cannot let them
spot any flaws.

04:35.480 --> 04:37.740
Maybe you shouldn't attend court today.

04:38.000 --> 04:39.730
Let's delay for a few more days.

04:41.920 --> 04:43.980
If the treaty is signed one day later,

04:45.430 --> 04:48.290
it gives our enemies
one more day to counterattack.

04:49.070 --> 04:51.800
By the time Xiahou Bo realizes
what's happening,

04:52.560 --> 04:54.290
we won't have the lead anymore.

04:54.750 --> 04:55.270
But...

04:56.000 --> 04:58.130
I know you're worried about my health,

04:58.360 --> 04:58.890
but look,

05:00.630 --> 05:02.430
the wound has stopped bleeding.

05:05.750 --> 05:08.150
If such a powerful poison
couldn't kill me,

05:08.680 --> 05:10.040
attending court

05:11.240 --> 05:12.700
is nothing to worry about.

05:14.390 --> 05:14.910
Your Majesty,

05:14.910 --> 05:16.240
Physician Xiao is here.

05:20.310 --> 05:21.510
If you don't trust me,

05:22.560 --> 05:23.690
surely you'll trust

05:24.080 --> 05:25.610
Physician Xiao's opinion?

05:35.600 --> 05:36.530
Physician Xiao,

05:37.270 --> 05:38.600
tell the Noble Consort—

05:38.870 --> 05:39.560
my wound

05:40.120 --> 05:41.580
is healing well, isn't it?

05:45.800 --> 05:48.060
Your Majesty's wound is indeed healing.

05:48.630 --> 05:49.960
Some moderate activity

05:50.510 --> 05:52.510
would help with blood circulation.

05:54.600 --> 05:54.920
See?

06:03.360 --> 06:04.420
Then make it quick.

06:05.240 --> 06:06.500
I'll wait for you here.

06:06.750 --> 06:07.560
That won't do.

06:09.510 --> 06:11.240
While I'm pretending at court,

06:11.480 --> 06:14.010
you need to go comfort the ladies
in the harem.

06:14.510 --> 06:16.040
We have to make it look real.

06:18.120 --> 06:19.360
Xie Yong'er did say

06:20.360 --> 06:21.760
that in these three days,

06:22.160 --> 06:22.950
my Zhaoyang Palace

06:22.950 --> 06:25.360
is being trampled upon
by all those women of yours.

06:25.360 --> 06:27.690
Then go quickly. What are you waiting for?

06:27.920 --> 06:30.560
I still need Physician Xiao
to change my dressing.

06:30.560 --> 06:31.600
I'm worried that—

06:32.040 --> 06:32.570
How about

06:35.310 --> 06:36.510
you help me change it?

06:38.630 --> 06:40.120
No one wants to help you with that.

06:40.120 --> 06:40.850
I'm leaving.

06:56.040 --> 06:56.360
Your Majesty!

06:56.360 --> 06:57.159
Your Majesty.

06:57.190 --> 06:57.990
Your Majesty.

07:00.120 --> 07:01.050
Physician Xiao.

07:04.530 --> 07:06.170
I have a favor to ask of you.

07:07.390 --> 07:08.990
Please speak, Your Majesty.

07:12.270 --> 07:13.870
Is there any strong medicine

07:15.270 --> 07:16.200
that can quickly

07:18.160 --> 07:19.560
boost energy and spirit?

07:25.120 --> 07:28.310
His Majesty arrives!

08:00.750 --> 08:04.040
Long live Your Majesty.

08:04.720 --> 08:06.120
Rise, my dear ministers.

08:06.560 --> 08:08.830
Thank you, Your Majesty.

08:14.510 --> 08:15.310
Your Majesty,

08:15.870 --> 08:17.400
after the trip to Mount Bei,

08:17.750 --> 08:20.410
we heard
the Empress Dowager suddenly fell ill.

08:20.480 --> 08:21.410
However, when we

08:21.630 --> 08:23.870
tried to visit, we were all turned away.

08:24.270 --> 08:24.870
Now,

08:25.600 --> 08:26.930
three days have passed,

08:27.630 --> 08:29.830
and rumors spread throughout the court

08:30.000 --> 08:32.330
that the Empress Dowager didn't fall ill.

08:34.200 --> 08:35.059
Then what is it?

08:36.549 --> 08:37.280
It's that...

08:39.549 --> 08:42.080
she was assassinated
by the Yan State envoys!

08:43.000 --> 08:43.929
Assassination?

08:44.600 --> 08:45.960
How did you know?

08:46.360 --> 08:47.290
Those Yan people

08:47.480 --> 08:48.450
massacred over

08:48.510 --> 08:50.970
50 of our soldiers
in front of the posthouse.

08:51.360 --> 08:53.150
Then they vanished without a trace.

08:53.150 --> 08:53.840
If not them,

08:54.150 --> 08:55.280
who else could it be?

08:58.240 --> 09:00.400
Lord Mu is truly well-informed.

09:00.550 --> 09:02.210
You even know the exact number

09:03.360 --> 09:04.630
of fallen soldiers.

09:15.720 --> 09:16.520
That's right.

09:17.480 --> 09:19.200
The Empress Dowager didn't fall ill.

09:19.200 --> 09:21.130
She was attacked by conspirators.

09:22.080 --> 09:23.030
After the shock,

09:23.790 --> 09:25.050
she suddenly took ill.

09:25.840 --> 09:27.600
And the mastermind is...

09:31.670 --> 09:33.600
Imperial Astronomer Yang Duojie.

09:37.630 --> 09:38.080
Yes.

09:38.630 --> 09:39.630
You're eloquent.

09:40.630 --> 09:42.560
Why don't you explain to everyone?

09:42.670 --> 09:43.030
Yes.

09:46.870 --> 09:47.670
Your Majesty,

09:48.120 --> 09:48.600
I

09:49.080 --> 09:50.600
observed celestial signs at night

09:50.600 --> 09:52.570
and discovered that
Imperial Guards Commander Zhao Wucheng

09:52.570 --> 09:53.960
harbored treasonous intentions.

09:53.960 --> 09:54.720
Three days ago,

09:54.720 --> 09:56.840
he deployed forces to raid the posthouse,

09:56.840 --> 09:58.550
attempting to kill the Yan envoys.

09:58.550 --> 10:01.430
He then personally led men
to Mount Bei for an assassination.

10:01.430 --> 10:02.230
Fortunately,

10:02.270 --> 10:03.720
I made calculations

10:04.240 --> 10:05.500
and anticipated this.

10:05.750 --> 10:07.870
Not only did I rescue
the Yan envoys in advance,

10:07.870 --> 10:09.500
but with their help,

10:09.630 --> 10:11.560
I also foiled Zhao Wucheng's plot.

10:12.240 --> 10:12.870
Although

10:14.640 --> 10:16.550
we paid a heavy price...

10:17.840 --> 10:18.700
Nevertheless,

10:19.390 --> 10:21.880
to honor the Empress Dowager's desire
for peace talks

10:21.880 --> 10:23.550
and not let it go to waste,

10:23.720 --> 10:26.240
I request Your Majesty to proceed
with peace talks immediately!

10:26.240 --> 10:26.770
Granted.

10:27.120 --> 10:27.670
Summon

10:27.750 --> 10:30.430
the Yan envoy!

10:50.480 --> 10:50.880
But...

10:51.120 --> 10:53.600
But we haven't gotten
to the bottom of this yet.

10:53.600 --> 10:55.660
We can't trust the Yan people!

10:55.840 --> 10:56.640
Your Majesty!

11:03.280 --> 11:04.880
I, Prince Tu'er of Yan State,

11:05.000 --> 11:06.930
pay respects to the Emperor of Xia!

11:14.110 --> 11:15.120
I never expected

11:15.630 --> 11:16.630
that Prince Tu'er

11:16.840 --> 11:19.120
would come in disguise himself.

11:19.720 --> 11:20.440
To be frank,

11:21.750 --> 11:23.720
I came under the Emperor of Yan's orders

11:23.720 --> 11:25.360
to not just sign the peace treaty

11:25.360 --> 11:28.950
but also to observe
your people's conditions and customs.

11:29.840 --> 11:31.390
I concealed my identity earlier

11:31.390 --> 11:32.700
to see

11:33.320 --> 11:34.790
what Great Xia truly looks like.

11:34.790 --> 11:36.150
So how did

11:36.330 --> 11:37.480
your investigation turn out?

11:37.480 --> 11:39.230
Your Majesty upheld justice

11:39.390 --> 11:40.360
at the Grand Longevity Banquet

11:40.360 --> 11:41.480
and restored our innocence.

11:41.480 --> 11:42.070
I believe

11:42.440 --> 11:44.790
your example inspires your people
to be equally loyal and righteous.

11:44.790 --> 11:46.150
The alliance between our two countries

11:46.150 --> 11:47.600
will surely be a long-lasting one.

11:47.600 --> 11:48.550
You flatter me.

11:49.480 --> 11:50.360
Prince Tu'er,

11:50.830 --> 11:52.230
you are brave and mighty,

11:52.250 --> 11:53.630
generous in your assistance,

11:53.630 --> 11:54.630
and truly someone

11:54.900 --> 11:56.500
I sincerely admire.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.150
You're too kind.

11:59.440 --> 12:01.320
Your Majesty is straightforward,

12:01.320 --> 12:02.050
and I, Tu'er,

12:02.440 --> 12:04.100
cannot be indecisive either.

12:04.480 --> 12:06.080
I've brought my official seal.

12:06.080 --> 12:07.390
Where is the peace treaty?

12:07.390 --> 12:08.720
Where should I stamp it?

12:27.630 --> 12:28.660
[Official Seal of Yan]

12:38.320 --> 12:38.910
Lord Mu.

12:42.600 --> 12:43.400
Your Majesty.

12:43.600 --> 12:45.800
The Empress Dowager values you highly.

12:46.170 --> 12:47.600
After court is dismissed,

12:47.600 --> 12:49.070
you shall lead everyone

12:49.320 --> 12:50.650
to convey this good news

12:50.840 --> 12:53.770
of the successful peace talk
to the Empress Dowager.

12:56.080 --> 12:56.600
I

12:57.720 --> 12:58.780
obey your command.

13:00.220 --> 13:01.080
Noble Consort.

13:01.510 --> 13:04.000
I've just learned
a fashionable peony makeup style.

13:04.000 --> 13:05.240
-Here. Have a try.
-No need.

13:05.240 --> 13:06.150
I already applied makeup this morning.

13:06.150 --> 13:06.840
Just try it.

13:07.630 --> 13:09.840
Our Noble Consort is absolutely gorgeous.

13:09.840 --> 13:11.120
If she wears heavy makeup,

13:11.120 --> 13:12.240
it would only diminish her beauty.

13:12.240 --> 13:15.480
Let me style your hair
in a simple cloud bun instead.

13:16.030 --> 13:16.490
No need.

13:16.550 --> 13:17.600
Styling hair is too troublesome.

13:17.600 --> 13:20.510
All these external things
are too superficial.

13:20.580 --> 13:23.260
The Noble Consort values inner beauty.

13:23.360 --> 13:26.390
Why not try my rose essence?

13:27.270 --> 13:28.600
It also sparks passion.

13:30.200 --> 13:30.810
Well,

13:31.200 --> 13:32.240
that's hardly necessary.

13:32.240 --> 13:33.320
It is necessary.

13:33.550 --> 13:34.440
If we have

13:34.440 --> 13:36.240
done anything wrong in the past,

13:36.240 --> 13:38.440
please don't hold it against us,
Your Highness.

13:38.440 --> 13:39.360
Not at all.

13:39.360 --> 13:40.550
What do you mean by that?

13:40.550 --> 13:41.550
Is our Noble Consort

13:41.550 --> 13:42.910
a petty person?

13:43.440 --> 13:44.050
Indeed.

13:47.910 --> 13:48.710
No, no.

13:48.790 --> 13:50.120
That's not what I meant.

13:50.150 --> 13:51.320
Then what did you mean?

13:51.320 --> 13:52.150
-She means...
-I—

13:52.150 --> 13:54.360
you didn't understand what she meant.

13:54.870 --> 13:56.260
What do you mean by that?

13:56.320 --> 13:57.440
-What are they arguing about?
-Hey!

13:57.440 --> 13:58.550
I didn't mean anything.

13:58.550 --> 13:59.150
What do you mean?

13:59.150 --> 14:00.440
-Stop arguing.
-What's wrong with me?

14:00.440 --> 14:01.200
All those things you did,

14:01.200 --> 14:01.750
I remember them all.

14:01.750 --> 14:02.270
All right, enough.

14:02.270 --> 14:03.600
What do you mean by that?

14:03.630 --> 14:04.910
You know perfectly well what I mean.

14:04.910 --> 14:07.000
-Consort Shu is the most jealous one.
-I didn't.

14:07.000 --> 14:07.600
Honestly speaking...

14:07.600 --> 14:08.440
You two were arguing,

14:08.440 --> 14:10.320
-why bring me into it?
-You guys are really interesting.

14:10.320 --> 14:13.270
I didn't say anything about you,
why are you talking about me?

14:13.270 --> 14:14.480
Noble Consort.

14:15.000 --> 14:18.000
A few days ago you asked me
to refurbish the courtyard,

14:18.630 --> 14:19.480
but

14:20.320 --> 14:21.630
it's impossible

14:22.150 --> 14:23.480
with just me alone.

14:23.670 --> 14:25.800
-Refurbish the courtyard?
-I didn't!

14:26.910 --> 14:27.770
Noble Consort,

14:28.320 --> 14:29.390
please don't worry.

14:29.390 --> 14:31.270
I excel at gardening.

14:32.670 --> 14:34.190
On my way here, I noticed

14:34.360 --> 14:35.630
the fish in this pond

14:35.720 --> 14:36.850
are of poor quality.

14:36.990 --> 14:39.050
They should all be replaced with koi.

14:39.510 --> 14:40.080
Kois!

14:40.150 --> 14:42.240
Please leave the carpentry work to me.

14:42.240 --> 14:44.440
After all, my grandfather
shares the same surname

14:44.440 --> 14:46.360
as one of the greatest carpenters.

14:46.360 --> 14:47.360
No need to work too hard!

14:47.360 --> 14:48.870
I don't have many talents,

14:49.270 --> 14:50.390
but I have plenty of money.

14:50.390 --> 14:51.390
For this renovation,

14:51.390 --> 14:52.720
there's no need to use
funds from the treasury.

14:52.720 --> 14:53.250
Use mine.

14:53.790 --> 14:54.480
Go on.

14:57.310 --> 14:57.840
Thank...

14:58.910 --> 14:59.720
Thank you all.

14:59.870 --> 15:00.330
You see,

15:00.840 --> 15:02.300
isn't the problem solved?

15:07.480 --> 15:08.080
Come on.

15:08.240 --> 15:08.900
Take a look.

15:08.960 --> 15:09.490
That one!

15:10.280 --> 15:10.630
Yes.

15:11.240 --> 15:11.910
Fish it up.

15:19.870 --> 15:20.800
What's going on?

15:21.650 --> 15:22.580
Why am I suddenly

15:22.750 --> 15:23.870
so popular?

15:26.030 --> 15:27.480
Once the Empress Dowager left,

15:27.480 --> 15:29.340
you, as the most favored consort,

15:29.720 --> 15:30.480
have naturally become

15:30.480 --> 15:31.480
the palace's CEO.

15:33.870 --> 15:34.960
But honestly,

15:36.240 --> 15:37.080
compared to all this

15:37.080 --> 15:38.910
cringe-worthy flattery,

15:39.360 --> 15:41.510
I actually miss the days
when they hated me.

15:41.510 --> 15:42.150
Of course.

15:42.500 --> 15:45.630
At least they weren't
tearing the place apart back then.

15:49.510 --> 15:50.080
My fish!

15:50.710 --> 15:51.650
Stop!

15:53.900 --> 15:54.500
It's over.

16:03.710 --> 16:04.840
I can't watch this anymore.

16:04.840 --> 16:05.720
You can enjoy this on your own.

16:05.720 --> 16:07.510
I'm going to look for Physician Xiao.

16:07.510 --> 16:08.320
Don't leave!

16:08.750 --> 16:09.480
Xie Yong'er!

16:09.670 --> 16:10.670
Reach down there!

16:11.780 --> 16:14.110
Is no one
going to do something about this?

16:38.630 --> 16:42.030
Greetings, Your Majesty.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.630
Rise.

16:56.640 --> 16:57.720
Her Majesty means

16:57.840 --> 16:59.530
for all of you to rise.

17:00.840 --> 17:02.240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

17:05.640 --> 17:06.980
Y-Your Majesty.

17:07.270 --> 17:08.329
Wh-What happened?

17:16.630 --> 17:17.990
Your Majesty,

17:19.200 --> 17:21.060
His Majesty asked me to inform you

17:21.440 --> 17:24.500
that the peace talks
have been successfully concluded

17:24.500 --> 17:25.900
and asks you not to worry.

17:31.400 --> 17:33.460
If the Your Majesty cannot speak,

17:33.920 --> 17:36.380
perhaps you could
write down your thoughts?

18:03.070 --> 18:03.870
Your Majesty?

18:03.880 --> 18:04.680
Your Majesty?

18:05.380 --> 18:06.910
Are you okay, Your Majesty?

18:16.070 --> 18:16.750
What is this?

18:16.750 --> 18:17.350
A shuttlecock.

18:17.350 --> 18:18.070
What's it for?

18:18.070 --> 18:18.800
For kicking.

18:19.000 --> 18:19.550
For whom?

18:19.790 --> 18:20.590
Us, of course.

18:20.590 --> 18:21.880
Why?

18:22.920 --> 18:23.950
I think

18:24.110 --> 18:25.830
in this palace,
everyone's always comparing looks,

18:25.830 --> 18:26.680
family background,

18:26.680 --> 18:27.720
and His Majesty's favor.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.850
The atmosphere is really unfriendly.

18:30.000 --> 18:30.680
Besides,

18:31.270 --> 18:32.350
throughout history,

18:32.350 --> 18:33.890
the concubines in the palace

18:33.890 --> 18:35.350
have had short lifespans.

18:35.440 --> 18:37.440
This situation is bad for everyone.

18:37.510 --> 18:37.880
So

18:38.360 --> 18:40.720
I've decided to introduce
shuttlecock kicking.

18:40.720 --> 18:42.070
Let's channel the competitive spirit

18:42.070 --> 18:43.930
into something more meaningful.

18:45.920 --> 18:47.240
And redirect your energy

18:47.240 --> 18:47.960
elsewhere.

18:48.590 --> 18:49.880
Stop always scheming against me.

18:49.510 --> 18:50.960
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

18:50.440 --> 18:51.030
But...

18:50.980 --> 18:52.600
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

18:51.270 --> 18:52.000
How do we...

18:52.000 --> 18:52.830
Kick...

18:52.960 --> 18:53.680
This shuttlecock?

18:52.970 --> 18:54.240
♪ Incredible ♪

18:54.440 --> 18:54.960
It's simple.

18:54.690 --> 18:55.810
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

18:55.310 --> 18:56.550
Let me show you.

18:56.340 --> 18:57.280
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

18:57.450 --> 18:59.050
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

18:57.640 --> 18:58.640
Watch carefully.

18:59.420 --> 19:00.580
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

19:01.020 --> 19:02.280
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

19:02.660 --> 19:05.440
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

19:05.720 --> 19:06.550
It's okay. I have more.

19:05.770 --> 19:07.360
♪ From day to night ♪

19:07.510 --> 19:08.940
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

19:09.030 --> 19:10.550
♪ From the present to the past ♪

19:10.700 --> 19:11.830
♪ It's always you ♪

19:11.440 --> 19:11.900
Come on.

19:12.160 --> 19:13.280
Follow what I just showed you.

19:12.320 --> 19:13.820
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

19:13.400 --> 19:14.140
Have a try.

19:13.840 --> 19:15.330
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

19:14.200 --> 19:15.400
Come on, Consort Shu.

19:15.410 --> 19:18.330
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

19:18.650 --> 19:21.750
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

19:21.810 --> 19:23.710
♪ With you ♪

19:24.220 --> 19:26.530
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

19:26.580 --> 19:28.140
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

19:28.210 --> 19:30.160
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

19:30.660 --> 19:33.010
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

19:33.060 --> 19:34.570
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

19:34.590 --> 19:36.610
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

19:35.200 --> 19:36.060
Good footwork!

19:37.720 --> 19:38.320
It's okay.

19:41.790 --> 19:42.250
Come on!

19:45.880 --> 19:47.030
It's boring

19:47.020 --> 19:48.490
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

19:47.160 --> 19:48.510
to play shuttlecock alone.

19:48.510 --> 19:49.830
It's meant to be played together.

19:48.630 --> 19:50.330
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

19:51.110 --> 19:52.370
Come on, form a circle.

19:54.720 --> 19:56.590
I'll pass it to you,
and you pass it to her.

19:56.590 --> 19:57.350
I'll try.

20:03.480 --> 20:04.700
♪ Incredible ♪

20:05.080 --> 20:06.260
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

20:05.960 --> 20:06.640
It's okay!

20:06.680 --> 20:07.710
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

20:06.760 --> 20:07.560
There's more.

20:07.790 --> 20:09.440
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

20:08.310 --> 20:09.070
Come on.

20:09.780 --> 20:10.980
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

20:11.450 --> 20:12.680
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

20:11.790 --> 20:12.650
Your Highness,

20:12.720 --> 20:14.220
can't we play somewhere else?

20:13.030 --> 20:15.890
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

20:14.680 --> 20:16.140
There's not much feather left.

20:16.140 --> 20:17.810
♪ From day to night ♪

20:16.400 --> 20:17.890
Chickens' lives matter too.

20:17.890 --> 20:19.420
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

20:19.480 --> 20:21.030
♪ From the present to the past ♪

20:21.070 --> 20:21.720
Sorry.

20:21.100 --> 20:22.210
♪ It's always you ♪

20:22.760 --> 20:24.190
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

20:24.260 --> 20:25.780
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

20:25.440 --> 20:27.270
But where can I find

20:25.810 --> 20:28.750
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

20:27.400 --> 20:29.590
a spacious and deserted place?

20:29.120 --> 20:32.160
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

20:32.250 --> 20:34.240
♪ With you ♪

20:32.510 --> 20:32.970
I got it!

20:34.640 --> 20:37.030
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

20:37.120 --> 20:38.620
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

20:38.690 --> 20:40.590
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

20:41.040 --> 20:43.390
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

20:43.420 --> 20:45.050
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

20:45.070 --> 20:47.000
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

20:51.050 --> 20:52.640
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

20:51.350 --> 20:52.560
Noble Consort Wei,

20:52.680 --> 20:54.290
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

20:53.480 --> 20:54.720
long time no see.

20:57.550 --> 20:57.960
Come.

20:58.030 --> 20:59.590
Move the heating brick inside,

20:59.590 --> 21:00.590
closer to the bed.

21:01.350 --> 21:01.750
Yes.

21:01.830 --> 21:02.200
Yes.

21:06.480 --> 21:07.550
Don't put it too close though,

21:07.550 --> 21:08.510
it'll be too hot.

21:12.590 --> 21:13.350
Madam Bei...

21:15.590 --> 21:16.590
Foot bath water!

21:16.720 --> 21:18.150
With hot water! Quick.

21:18.240 --> 21:19.440
-Coming.
-Steady.

21:19.920 --> 21:20.550
Mr. Bei.

21:21.550 --> 21:22.810
-Don't fall.
-Mr. Bei.

21:23.400 --> 21:24.530
In this cold winter,

21:24.680 --> 21:27.140
water will freeze
if you drip it on the floor.

21:28.640 --> 21:29.640
Please talk to me.

21:32.310 --> 21:33.350
-Madam Bei.
-All right.

21:33.350 --> 21:34.680
All of you may leave now.

21:37.110 --> 21:37.640
Mr. Bei.

21:40.790 --> 21:41.400
Mr. Bei!

21:48.880 --> 21:49.880
I was wrong

21:51.310 --> 21:52.840
for what I did this morning.

21:54.550 --> 21:55.480
But at that time,

21:57.550 --> 21:59.080
I truly had no other choice.

21:59.880 --> 22:01.280
Do you know how much blood

22:01.480 --> 22:02.210
you've lost?

22:03.030 --> 22:04.490
Not resting is bad enough,

22:04.960 --> 22:06.750
but you dare to use
such dangerous methods.

22:06.750 --> 22:08.680
You really don't care about your life.

22:08.680 --> 22:09.440
I know

22:11.030 --> 22:12.070
you care about me.

22:14.960 --> 22:16.350
But in that situation—

22:16.350 --> 22:17.280
What situation?

22:17.720 --> 22:18.270
No matter what situation it was,

22:18.270 --> 22:20.870
you shouldn't have
taken your life so lightly!

22:22.000 --> 22:23.200
I've told you before,

22:23.790 --> 22:24.640
Nan's child

22:25.440 --> 22:26.400
is my child too.

22:27.820 --> 22:28.950
In this world, I have

22:29.310 --> 22:30.840
no family and no relatives.

22:31.030 --> 22:32.880
The reason I protect you with all my might

22:32.880 --> 22:34.830
is not for any grand cause
of the country or family.

22:34.830 --> 22:37.110
If you dare risk your life again

22:37.110 --> 22:38.310
for this darn throne,

22:38.590 --> 22:39.030
I...

22:39.480 --> 22:41.270
I will tie you up and take you away!

22:41.270 --> 22:42.330
Do you understand?

22:44.200 --> 22:45.000
I understand.

22:48.920 --> 22:50.250
You care for me the most.

22:51.110 --> 22:51.590
I know.

22:54.550 --> 22:56.150
Stop with these sweet words.

22:57.030 --> 22:57.830
They don't work

22:57.830 --> 22:58.290
with me.

23:10.440 --> 23:10.950
Let me see!

23:10.950 --> 23:12.550
Is your wound hurting again?

23:13.590 --> 23:14.200
Mr. Bei...

23:16.000 --> 23:17.260
This water is a bit hot.

23:18.640 --> 23:19.700
You're so naughty!

23:22.590 --> 23:24.090
Come, cover up properly.

23:24.400 --> 23:25.460
Don't catch a cold.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.470
Let me wash it for you.

23:29.790 --> 23:30.920
Bring your feet out.

23:36.200 --> 23:38.130
Isn't the temperature just right?

23:38.350 --> 23:40.110
Hot water drives away the cold.

23:49.030 --> 23:49.750
Mr. Bei...

23:53.000 --> 23:54.070
If only...

23:56.350 --> 23:58.410
you and Wanyin had appeared earlier.

24:01.030 --> 24:03.030
How wonderful that would have been.

24:09.270 --> 24:10.270
I want to play too.

24:21.190 --> 24:22.030
So impressive!

24:22.030 --> 24:23.290
Who would have thought

24:23.400 --> 24:25.730
Noble Consort Wei would be such an expert?

24:26.920 --> 24:28.270
Now that I've taught my apprentice,

24:28.270 --> 24:29.600
I'm useless as a master—

24:30.040 --> 24:31.630
no wonder that's a saying.

24:31.840 --> 24:32.430
She's so good.

24:32.430 --> 24:33.290
Your Highness.

24:33.480 --> 24:34.840
Are we returning to the palace

24:34.840 --> 24:36.170
or going to His Majesty?

24:36.880 --> 24:38.210
Let's go to His Majesty.

24:38.310 --> 24:38.640
Yes.

24:41.880 --> 24:43.080
The palace is so huge.

24:43.200 --> 24:44.930
Why isn't there bike-sharing?

24:45.830 --> 24:47.750
Isn't there a shortcut?

24:50.350 --> 24:51.150
You're right!

24:51.270 --> 24:51.900
Like this?

25:06.240 --> 25:07.160
Just admit it.

25:07.350 --> 25:09.610
Seeing a bunch of women fighting for you—

25:10.440 --> 25:12.770
you're secretly enjoying it, aren't you?

25:14.790 --> 25:15.880
You're turning your head away?

25:15.880 --> 25:17.010
What does that mean?

25:17.030 --> 25:18.790
I know men too well.

25:19.350 --> 25:20.440
You say no,

25:21.030 --> 25:23.230
but inside you're probably delighted.

25:27.400 --> 25:27.960
Fine.

25:29.510 --> 25:30.920
I admit I'm jealous.

25:32.790 --> 25:33.790
Sorry about that.

26:01.300 --> 26:01.870
Let's go.

26:02.180 --> 26:03.240
What are you doing?

26:03.680 --> 26:04.680
I'm stuck.

26:04.920 --> 26:05.800
Look at you.

26:06.270 --> 26:07.670
You call yourself a hero?

26:07.750 --> 26:08.480
Hero?

26:08.830 --> 26:10.500
More like your scapegoat!

26:15.070 --> 26:16.030
Bai...

26:27.980 --> 26:29.720
You don't snore, do you?

26:30.030 --> 26:32.200
If you're afraid of noise,
go sleep upstairs.

26:32.200 --> 26:33.030
Dream on.

27:04.960 --> 27:05.490
How nice.

27:11.350 --> 27:12.150
Your Majesty,

27:12.750 --> 27:14.750
the Imperial Medical Bureau
is now focusing

27:14.750 --> 27:17.150
entirely on treating the Empress Dowager,

27:17.310 --> 27:19.240
but the results aren't promising.

27:19.830 --> 27:21.830
If they can't handle it, you step in.

27:22.590 --> 27:24.240
Make sure the Empress Dowager

27:24.240 --> 27:25.640
can hold on for one month.

27:25.830 --> 27:26.380
Yes.

27:38.400 --> 27:39.800
What do you plan to do now?

27:43.840 --> 27:45.450
What's with that look?

27:45.750 --> 27:47.410
What kind of attitude is that?

27:48.840 --> 27:50.240
I know you don't trust me.

27:50.440 --> 27:51.790
If it weren't for Yu Wanyin,

27:51.790 --> 27:53.390
I wouldn't trust you either.

27:53.960 --> 27:54.830
But I'm telling you,

27:54.830 --> 27:55.900
we're allies now.

27:56.310 --> 27:57.970
If you don't tell me your plan,

27:58.270 --> 27:59.870
how can I cooperate with you?

28:06.430 --> 28:07.920
If the Empress Dowager doesn't die,

28:07.920 --> 28:08.780
those factions

28:09.030 --> 28:10.560
will keep their hopes alive

28:11.000 --> 28:13.530
and won't immediately
side with Prince Duan.

28:13.720 --> 28:14.590
You mean

28:15.070 --> 28:17.510
you want to win over
the Empress Dowager's faction,

28:17.510 --> 28:19.040
stabilize the court first,

28:19.310 --> 28:20.590
then settle scores later?

28:20.590 --> 28:21.790
You figured that out?

28:22.830 --> 28:24.310
Not bad.

28:25.070 --> 28:27.510
Yu Wanyin said
you've only been here half a year,

28:27.510 --> 28:29.750
but the way you use these imperial tactics

28:29.750 --> 28:31.950
doesn't look like you're acting at all.

28:33.510 --> 28:35.240
I'll take that as a compliment.

28:35.590 --> 28:37.120
But your plan has one flaw.

28:37.880 --> 28:39.720
There's a troublemaker
in the Empress Dowager's faction

28:39.720 --> 28:40.450
named Mu Yun.

28:40.920 --> 28:42.520
You must get rid of him first.

28:42.720 --> 28:43.980
Or the plan won't work.

28:45.780 --> 28:47.140
The self-torture ruse,

28:47.640 --> 28:48.840
the chain stratagem,

28:49.270 --> 28:51.270
and the counter-espionage tactic.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.480
My brother

28:53.480 --> 28:55.480
has really studied "The Art of War."

28:56.130 --> 28:58.260
He's even using double agent tactics.

28:58.590 --> 28:59.920
So what do you plan to do?

29:00.490 --> 29:01.090
Kill him?

29:03.000 --> 29:04.600
That would be too easy on him.

29:07.830 --> 29:09.290
Stir-fry him on high heat,

29:09.960 --> 29:11.490
then simmer him on low heat.

29:12.240 --> 29:13.770
Now that his cover's blown,

29:14.830 --> 29:16.290
there are plenty of people

29:16.790 --> 29:18.050
eager to deal with him.

29:23.660 --> 29:25.730
I knew you were a tyrant.

29:30.850 --> 29:32.200
If there's nothing else,

29:32.200 --> 29:33.400
I shall take my leave.

29:34.720 --> 29:35.780
Farewell, my dear.

29:36.750 --> 29:37.240
Tyrant.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.740
How long do you plan to eavesdrop?

30:00.070 --> 30:01.590
I wasn't just checking up on you.

30:01.590 --> 30:03.450
Just wanted to take the shortcut.

30:05.920 --> 30:08.120
Why do you look worse than this morning?

30:10.070 --> 30:12.240
Before and after makeup
make a huge difference.

30:12.240 --> 30:13.070
Liar.

30:13.960 --> 30:15.690
Things didn't go well at court?

30:16.110 --> 30:16.840
It went well—

30:17.350 --> 30:18.270
very well.

30:19.550 --> 30:20.410
What about you?

30:21.790 --> 30:23.240
It's a long story.

30:31.350 --> 30:32.150
What's wrong?

30:32.720 --> 30:34.270
How come
after being out for the whole day,

30:34.270 --> 30:35.290
you smell so good?

30:37.240 --> 30:39.830
Concubine He
just sprayed me with rose essence.

30:39.830 --> 30:42.610
Why not try my handmade rose essence?

30:43.200 --> 30:44.600
It also sparks passion.

30:44.750 --> 30:45.510
No wonder.

30:47.480 --> 30:48.880
It's driving me crazy.

30:49.920 --> 30:51.520
I'm talking about serious matters.

30:51.520 --> 30:52.920
This is a serious matter.

30:54.200 --> 30:54.960
No.

30:55.510 --> 30:56.310
Just one kiss.

30:57.200 --> 30:58.720
Control yourself!

31:03.010 --> 31:04.250
Oh, one more thing—

31:09.830 --> 31:10.200
I...

31:11.920 --> 31:12.480
Well...

31:22.340 --> 31:23.380
How immoral.

31:23.590 --> 31:24.800
How unethical.

31:25.110 --> 31:26.310
No bottom line at all.

31:26.670 --> 31:27.810
Shameless.

31:28.440 --> 31:29.970
They know nothing but love!

31:30.720 --> 31:31.950
I won't be like you—

31:32.920 --> 31:33.780
Your Highness!

31:34.360 --> 31:36.160
Your Highness, are you alright?

31:36.480 --> 31:37.940
Imperial Physician Xiao?

31:38.430 --> 31:39.280
Careful.

31:39.640 --> 31:40.830
That hurt.

31:43.240 --> 31:44.640
Why haven't you left yet?

31:45.640 --> 31:46.680
I was thinking

31:46.830 --> 31:48.510
the palace is unsafe right now.

31:48.510 --> 31:49.570
It's getting late,

31:49.570 --> 31:51.830
and it's not safe for you to return alone.

31:52.310 --> 31:54.110
You've been waiting here for me?

32:08.680 --> 32:10.140
Imperial Physician Xiao,

32:10.310 --> 32:11.770
you have something to say?

32:17.320 --> 32:18.780
Imperial Physician Xiao.

32:18.960 --> 32:20.290
I consider you a friend.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.740
You can be yourself
in front of me.

32:23.580 --> 32:25.180
Feel free to speak your mind.

32:28.260 --> 32:29.240
Consort Xie,

32:30.370 --> 32:31.480
there's something

32:31.680 --> 32:32.810
I don't understand.

32:37.640 --> 32:38.920
You're wondering

32:40.070 --> 32:40.790
how before,

32:41.320 --> 32:44.310
I hated His Majesty
so much I wanted to abort his child,

32:44.310 --> 32:46.440
but now I'm running around everywhere

32:46.610 --> 32:47.940
trying to save his life?

32:48.550 --> 32:49.350
Is that right?

32:55.830 --> 32:57.270
Imperial Physician Xiao.

32:57.270 --> 32:57.870
I'm sorry.

32:58.750 --> 32:59.880
I lied to you before.

33:00.900 --> 33:02.830
Your Highness, what are you doing?

33:04.590 --> 33:05.480
That child

33:06.640 --> 33:07.700
was Prince Duan's.

33:08.110 --> 33:08.570
Prince—

33:13.310 --> 33:14.170
Your Highness.

33:14.470 --> 33:16.230
You must never speak of this.

33:16.750 --> 33:18.590
If word gets out, it's a capital offense.

33:18.590 --> 33:19.650
His Majesty knows.

33:19.790 --> 33:20.120
He...

33:26.880 --> 33:27.830
He knows?

33:28.790 --> 33:29.410
Yes.

33:31.960 --> 33:33.310
The power struggles at court

33:33.310 --> 33:34.570
are no longer a secret.

33:35.550 --> 33:36.990
Before, to survive

33:37.070 --> 33:38.530
and for personal reasons,

33:38.880 --> 33:40.500
I made some wrong choices.

33:41.310 --> 33:43.440
I've tasted backlash
of my own making.

33:44.480 --> 33:47.440
Thankfully, His Majesty
and the Noble Consort are willing to help.

33:47.440 --> 33:48.500
I've also realized

33:48.790 --> 33:50.650
that Prince Duan is not a good man.

33:51.440 --> 33:53.240
So rest assured, Imperial Physician Xiao.

33:53.240 --> 33:54.170
I'm safe for now.

33:54.640 --> 33:55.720
F-For now?

33:58.790 --> 34:02.390
What about after His Majesty
and Prince Duan settle their score?

34:05.110 --> 34:06.030
Perhaps

34:07.510 --> 34:09.310
I'll need to find a way to escape?

34:14.030 --> 34:15.350
Isn't it funny?

34:16.280 --> 34:18.280
I wanted to possess the whole world,

34:19.190 --> 34:21.449
but I'm trapped within these high walls.

34:22.230 --> 34:23.630
I didn't even know

34:25.960 --> 34:27.489
what the world looked like.

34:49.150 --> 34:50.949
My dear, were you waiting for me?

34:54.800 --> 34:55.150
Come,

34:56.630 --> 34:57.190
My sir,

34:58.280 --> 34:59.410
take your medicine.

35:02.490 --> 35:05.630
I've already taken the medicine
Imperial Physician Xiao gave me.

35:05.630 --> 35:08.070
I spent two hours brewing this,

35:08.670 --> 35:10.330
waiting for you to finish work

35:10.440 --> 35:13.170
so you could drink
this cooling tonic right away.

35:15.150 --> 35:16.230
I don't think that's necessary.

35:16.230 --> 35:17.030
How so?

35:17.710 --> 35:19.370
You're fighting all day long.

35:19.480 --> 35:20.320
If you don't drink it,

35:20.320 --> 35:21.380
you won't survive.

35:24.590 --> 35:25.990
What was it I forgot to do?

35:27.920 --> 35:28.280
The memorials!

35:28.280 --> 35:28.810
Drink it.

35:34.590 --> 35:35.760
Fine, fine.

35:40.590 --> 35:41.720
That's more like it.

35:44.920 --> 35:45.580
It's sweet?

35:47.760 --> 35:49.280
Chrysanthemum with rock sugar—

35:49.280 --> 35:50.480
of course it's sweet.

35:58.280 --> 35:59.880
You're so good to me, my dear.

36:01.840 --> 36:02.240
You...

36:03.280 --> 36:05.620
Why are you still so irritable?

36:05.840 --> 36:07.320
If you have energy, take it out on work.

36:07.320 --> 36:08.700
Didn't you say there are
memorials left to review?

36:08.700 --> 36:09.100
Go.

36:09.800 --> 36:11.590
There are too many. I can't finish them.

36:11.590 --> 36:12.070
CEO Dan,

36:12.400 --> 36:14.200
I have to criticize you for this.

36:16.070 --> 36:17.590
Why do you think you're a bad actor?

36:17.590 --> 36:19.150
You don't read enough books.

36:19.150 --> 36:20.920
No matter what industry you're in,

36:20.920 --> 36:22.710
you require general knowledge.

36:22.710 --> 36:23.940
Just a few memorials

36:24.070 --> 36:24.920
got you good?

36:25.630 --> 36:26.490
If you can do it,

36:27.030 --> 36:27.830
then you do it.

36:29.510 --> 36:31.310
I'm a seasoned corporate slave.

36:32.150 --> 36:33.410
This little bit of work

36:33.550 --> 36:35.410
can be solved with some overtime.

36:35.480 --> 36:36.480
Don't provoke me.

36:37.510 --> 36:39.320
This little bit of work?

36:43.670 --> 36:44.480
Eunuch An,

36:45.310 --> 36:47.310
bring up the unreviewed memorials.

36:51.580 --> 36:52.380
Your Majesty,

36:52.670 --> 36:53.700
these just arrived.

36:53.700 --> 36:55.830
And there's still half more on the way.

36:59.670 --> 37:00.250
Well...

37:01.270 --> 37:03.070
I suddenly have something to do.

37:03.070 --> 37:03.800
My dear.

37:05.920 --> 37:07.030
Don't make me

37:07.800 --> 37:09.130
anxious and irritable.

37:14.070 --> 37:14.530
Well...

37:15.960 --> 37:17.230
is there overtime pay?

37:24.190 --> 37:25.280
Grand Mentor Zhang

37:26.190 --> 37:27.920
praised you 300 times,

37:28.710 --> 37:31.370
but the main point
was to boast about his nephew?

37:31.840 --> 37:34.290
There's flooding in J-Jiangnan.

37:32.180 --> 37:35.730
[Grand Mentor Zhang's nephew]

37:34.640 --> 37:36.340
S-So...

37:35.740 --> 37:37.190
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

37:37.150 --> 37:38.670
I-I think...

37:37.210 --> 37:38.830
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

37:38.800 --> 37:39.510
Stop thinking.

37:39.200 --> 37:40.470
♪ Incredible ♪

37:40.360 --> 37:41.110
Listening to you gives me a headache.

37:40.920 --> 37:42.090
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

37:42.510 --> 37:43.260
Drag him out.

37:42.570 --> 37:43.550
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

37:43.680 --> 37:45.280
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

37:43.760 --> 37:45.650
Bring someone who can speak properly.

37:45.650 --> 37:46.810
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

37:46.320 --> 37:47.630
Y-Y-Y-Your Majesty!

37:47.250 --> 37:48.510
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

37:47.630 --> 37:50.400
Vice Minister Yang, Grand Commandant Lu,
and Minister Gou

37:48.890 --> 37:51.780
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

37:51.320 --> 37:53.000
also submitted memorials

37:52.000 --> 37:53.650
♪ From day to night ♪

37:53.190 --> 37:54.920
threatening to retire.

37:53.740 --> 37:55.170
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

37:55.260 --> 37:56.830
♪ From the present to the past ♪

37:55.580 --> 37:56.320
Your Majesty!

37:55.780 --> 37:58.760
[Grand Commandant Lu] [Vice Minister Yang]
[Minister Gou]

37:56.760 --> 37:57.800
If this goes on,

37:56.930 --> 37:58.100
♪ It's always you ♪

37:58.030 --> 37:59.070
a country will no longer be like a country,

37:58.550 --> 38:00.050
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

37:59.630 --> 38:03.840
and I will be too ashamed
to accept the salary you provide.

38:00.070 --> 38:01.760
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

38:01.790 --> 38:04.710
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

38:03.960 --> 38:04.920
Then...

38:05.070 --> 38:08.170
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

38:06.960 --> 38:07.880
return it to me.

38:08.230 --> 38:10.170
♪ With you ♪

38:09.510 --> 38:10.880
The treasury happens to be low on funds.

38:10.640 --> 38:12.950
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

38:11.150 --> 38:12.030
My lords,

38:12.150 --> 38:13.880
you truly understand my concerns.

38:13.000 --> 38:14.560
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

38:14.630 --> 38:16.580
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

38:17.080 --> 38:19.430
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

38:19.070 --> 38:19.590
This

38:19.480 --> 38:20.990
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

38:19.880 --> 38:20.590
and these—

38:21.010 --> 38:23.140
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

38:21.320 --> 38:22.480
they are ambiguous.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.700
They're clearly fence-sitters.

38:26.400 --> 38:27.000
Is that so?

38:28.760 --> 38:30.360
Then let's send a gust of wind

38:30.480 --> 38:32.200
to make them fall to our side.

38:32.320 --> 38:34.070
The Minister of Revenue, Chen Danian,

38:33.650 --> 38:35.150
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

38:34.190 --> 38:35.430
is loyal.

38:35.250 --> 38:36.990
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

38:35.800 --> 38:37.670
The Vice Minister of Works, Wei Hongyu,

38:37.670 --> 38:39.000
is clever and decisive.

38:39.320 --> 38:41.360
The Chief of the State Ceremonial Bureau,
Gu Tingzhi,

38:41.360 --> 38:42.760
is rigorous and upright.

38:42.920 --> 38:44.760
The Director of the Ministry of War,
Wu Jiadong,

38:44.760 --> 38:46.230
is brave and loyal.

38:46.670 --> 38:47.870
You are all promoted!

38:48.710 --> 38:50.480
Your Majesty is wise!

38:50.200 --> 38:51.420
♪ Incredible ♪

38:51.320 --> 38:52.760
Li Yunxi also submitted a memorial.

38:51.810 --> 38:53.070
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

38:53.390 --> 38:54.420
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

38:53.840 --> 38:54.880
Didn't I tell him

38:54.500 --> 38:56.210
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

38:55.030 --> 38:57.380
not to show up at this critical time

38:56.490 --> 38:57.780
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

38:58.150 --> 39:00.070
so people won't think of him
as an imperial loyalist?

38:58.160 --> 38:59.430
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

38:59.850 --> 39:02.710
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

39:01.960 --> 39:02.880
Don't worry.

39:02.960 --> 39:04.630
♪ From day to night ♪

39:03.590 --> 39:04.670
This time he has

39:04.670 --> 39:06.550
miraculously understood your intentions.

39:04.710 --> 39:06.240
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

39:06.300 --> 39:07.850
♪ From the present to the past ♪

39:07.920 --> 39:09.030
♪ It's always you ♪

39:08.110 --> 39:10.540
He knows you want him and those scholars

39:09.580 --> 39:11.010
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

39:10.960 --> 39:13.670
to appear resentful for not being valued.

39:11.080 --> 39:12.670
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

39:12.720 --> 39:15.640
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

39:14.110 --> 39:16.000
So even if Prince Duan gains power,

39:16.000 --> 39:19.040
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

39:16.510 --> 39:18.400
he won't hold grudges against them.

39:18.400 --> 39:19.190
So...

39:19.130 --> 39:21.120
♪ With you ♪

39:21.600 --> 39:23.990
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

39:24.080 --> 39:25.580
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

39:25.650 --> 39:27.550
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

39:28.080 --> 39:30.430
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

39:28.760 --> 39:30.460
Your Majesty is shortsighted,

39:30.460 --> 39:32.090
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

39:30.510 --> 39:32.110
and you don't know how to use people.

39:32.110 --> 39:34.040
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

39:32.150 --> 39:33.440
You are incompetent and foolish.

39:33.440 --> 39:34.670
How inappropriate!

39:37.760 --> 39:38.520
I said

39:39.120 --> 39:41.120
there's no need to act too friendly.

39:41.320 --> 39:43.580
But that's no reason for him to insult me!

39:44.580 --> 39:46.170
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

39:45.040 --> 39:46.210
My predicament's funny?

39:46.210 --> 39:47.820
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

39:47.360 --> 39:48.210
You were insulted too.

39:48.210 --> 39:49.400
♪ The wind is blowing gently ♪

39:49.610 --> 39:50.910
♪ Bringing news ♪

39:51.080 --> 39:52.570
♪ About your whereabouts ♪

39:52.630 --> 39:54.240
♪ Guiding me far away ♪

39:53.400 --> 39:55.150
You ruin the country and the people

39:54.610 --> 39:55.780
♪ I carefully ♪

39:55.440 --> 39:56.630
and dote on the demonic consort.

39:56.050 --> 39:57.560
♪ Collect time ♪

39:57.360 --> 39:58.680
You spend all day

39:57.900 --> 39:59.560
♪ I'll hide it well ♪

39:58.920 --> 40:00.140
with a beauty.

39:59.760 --> 40:02.240
♪ The secret of meeting you ♪

40:00.440 --> 40:01.570
How inappropriate!

40:03.590 --> 40:05.010
These are compliments.

40:06.710 --> 40:08.240
Whatever floats your boat.

40:09.540 --> 40:10.370
An Xian, clean this up.

40:10.330 --> 40:11.880
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

40:11.950 --> 40:13.710
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪
